    FutureFeature
    Annotation to represent future feature which is not ready for the current platform release.
    MandatoryFeature
    This is for mandatory features.
    OptionalFeature
    This is for optional features.
    RequiredFeature
    Annotation to represent a feature required to use the specified method.

    Annotation for specifying value type for key - value pair.
